{"div":{"@xmlns":"http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0","@type":"article","@xml:id":"MG-1702-01_140","head":{"value":"[Rondeau]","id":"/div/head"},"bibl":{"title":{"value":"Mercure galant","id":"/div/bibl/title"},"#":{"value":", janvier 1702 [tome 1], p. 140-142.","id":"/div/bibl/#"}},"p":{"#1":{"value":"M","id":"/div/p/#1"},"hi":{"@rend":"sup","#":{"value":"r","id":"/div/p/hi/#"}},"#2":{"value":" Alison est Autheur de ces Vers, aussi bien que du Rondeau que vous allez lire. Il le fit à l’occasion d’une Dame qui fuyoit le commerce des hommes, &amp; qu’on accusoit cependant d’avoir beaucoup de penchant pour un Cavalier qui l’aimoit passionnément. Il fait parler la Dame.","id":"/div/p/#2"}},"quote":{"#":[{"label":{"value":"RONDEAU.","id":"/div/quote/#[0]/label"}},{"lg":{"l":[{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Tendres Desirs naissent sans qu’on y pense ;","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[0]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ecoutât-on long-temps sans preference","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[1]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"De maints Amans les plaintes &amp; douceurs :","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[2]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"L’Amour souvent se glisse dans les cœurs","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[3]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Par le secours d’une telle indolence.","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[4]/hi/#"}}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[2]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Aussi le mien, crainte de dépendance","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[0]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"De tels essais ne fait experience.","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[1]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ainsi ne craint, loin des hommes trompeurs,","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[2]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[3]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Tendres Desirs.","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[3]/hi/#"}}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[4]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Mais si Damon dont je plains la souffrance","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[0]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Me surprenoit, malgré ma prévoyance,","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[1]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Dans un lieu propre aux timides ardeurs ;","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[2]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Au doux recit de ses tristes langueurs,","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[3]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Pourrois-je bien vous faire resistance,","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[4]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[5]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Tendres Desirs ?","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[5]/hi/#"}}}]}}]}}}